               <p>I lost a policat handkerchief on the 14th of this month, in <placeName id="t17900526-11-crimeloc56">Smithfield</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-11-crimeloc56" type="placeName" value="Smithfield"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-11-crimeloc56" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-11-off54 t17900526-11-crimeloc56"></join>, out of my pocket: I was standing seeing a man breaking in a horse: the prisoner came running up, and pushed me, and ran away; it struck me he was at no good; and I felt to my pocket, and I found my handkerchief gone; I hallooed stop thief! and pursued him; and a man stopped him, who is here; he<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179005260019"></xptr>was searched; at the time he was laid hold of, he was putting it in his breeches; I saw it taken from him; the man has got it here.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. He dropped it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900526-11-person154">
                  JOHN
                   NEWMAN
               <interp inst="t17900526-11-person154" type="surname" value="NEWMAN"></interp>
