                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I stopped the prisoner; I took the handkerchief out of his breeches: (produces the handkerchief:) this is the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. This is mine; it is marked 
               <persName id="t17900526-11-person155">
                  R. 
               <interp inst="t17900526-11-person155" type="given" value="R."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900526-11-person155" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                  </persName>
            A. No. 7.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>This handkerchief was valued at one shilling at Guild-hall, and now it is valued at four shillings: I have no witnesses: I was taken at a disadvantage, all in a minute.</p>
